Brian was initially developed starting in 2022 by a team at EDF,
including, with various roles and levels of involvement:

- Kent Brudey <kent-externe.brudey@edf.fr>
- Clément Chazalet <clement.chazalet@edf.fr>
- Roland Mas <lolando@debian.org>
- Karim Mogaadi <karim-externe.mogaadi@edf.fr>
- Maxime Prost <maxime.prost@edf.fr>
- Luca Soler <luca.soler@edf.fr>
- Lucas Vitorino <lucas.vitorino@edf.fr>

It was renamed to Jenny when it was made public, because there was
already a piece of software called Brian.

